If you get the message "Could not location a valid installation of Call of Duty".:

Open regedit.exe.

Add key "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINESOFTWAREActivisionCall of Duty"

Add a string value with the name "InstallPath" there with the value of your installation.

== REG FILE =====

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINESOFTWAREActivisionCall of Duty]
"InstallPath"="C:\Pub\Games\Call of Duty"
